description: Number of 2n-bead black-white complementable strings with n black beads and fundamental period 2n.
comments: For n>0, a(n) is divisible by n (cf. A022553), 2*a(n) is divisible by n^2 (cf. A268619), and 12*a(n) is divisible by n^3 (cf. A268592). - _Max Alekseyev_, Feb 07 2016
formula: Moebius transform of A001700(n-1). - _Christian G. Bower_.For n>0, a(n) = A007727(n)/2 = n * A022553(n).
author: _David W. Wilson_
